| TC ID | Scenario                     | Expected Result             |
| ----- | ---------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| TC001 | Login with valid credentials | User logged in successfully |
| TC002 | Invalid Password             | Error message displayed     |
| TC003 | Invalid Username             | Error message displayed     |
| TC004 | Empty Username               | Validation message          |
| TC005 | Empty Password               | Validation message          |
| TC006 | Both fields empty            | Validation message          |
| TC007 | Password Case Sensitivity    | System validates correctly  |
| TC008 | Session Timeout              | User redirected to login    |
